Details

Question Here is a list of some of the ways in which people are connected to each other. Some people can be connected to you In more than one way. For example, a man could be your brother and he may belong to your church and be your lawyer. When I read you a name, please tell me all the ways that person is connected to you. How is (NAME) connected to you? PROBE: What other ways? ASK FOR EACH NAME. F2. Second Person is Co-Worker
